verbose_text: The frequency of high expression DPP4 (DPP4 +) monocytes in the peripheral blood (XREF_FIG) and DPP4 expression level as indicated by DPP4 mean fluorescence intensity (MFI) on circulating monocytes (XREF_FIG) were increased in patients with atherosclerosis, even after adjusting for obesity and current prescription drug therapy (ACE inhibitors and angiotensin receptor blockers).
